HEADWORD: Water milfoil
<hw>Wa"ter mil"foil</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Any plant
of the genus <gen>Myriophyllum</gen>, aquatic herbs with whorled leaves,
the submersed ones pinnately parted into capillary divisions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

